metadata.description: Dennis the Menace - The World's Wildest Boy - and his faithful Abyssinian Wire-Haired Tripe-Hound, Gnasher, run wild, run riot, and run rings round grown-ups (and other annoying pests) in their Menacing Mission to make Beanotown the place where kids rule!
metadata.name: The Beano presents Dennis the Menace and Gnasher
